  <id>dev.sarkis.time-manager</id>
  <name>Skopii</name>
  <summary>Manage your time and track project profitability</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      This Time Manager application is designed to help employees and freelancers track their working hours, breaks, and projects, providing a detailed breakdown of how much time is invested in each project. Additionally, it offers cost tracking to calculate profits based on a custom hourly rate.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Track working hours and breaks</li>
      <li>Project-based time tracking</li>
      <li>Cost calculation with custom hourly rates</li>
      <li>Work pattern analysis</li>
      <li>Project profitability tracking</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
